{"about_the_game":"<strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> is an RPG job system arena fighter featuring a huge roster of over 60 character classes to battle with. Drawing inspiration from JRPG favorites and the competitive classics of console multiplayer, players progress through 8 intensifying rounds of fierce combat, gain new abilities each round and build up their arsenals to the top of the class tree.<br><br>To bolster the slash/thrust/parry weapons-based melee, every player pairs the new ability of their chosen job with one earned from an earlier job for an ever-evolving, two-fisted loadout. <i>With up to 4 players mixing &amp; matching, the possibilities are sprawling!</i><br><br>The fight gets fleshed out further by <strong>bots</strong>, <strong>teams</strong>, <strong>custom scoring</strong>, <strong>deeply tweakable procedurally generated battlefields</strong> and beyond with additional gameplay options.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_anim_02.gif?t=1653929076\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><strong>GCM2</strong> offers a highly-customizable multiplayer brawl supporting up to 4 players on gamepads &amp; keyboard.  Play online with friends via Remote Play.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Features currently available include:</u></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>'Critters'</strong> wander each biome, dropping a heart when killed (live as of v1.1.7!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Selection Hiding'</strong> to prevent opponents from counter-picking classes (live as of v1.1.4!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Terrain Generation Customization'</strong> that gives players the power to deeply customize the terrain generator (live as of v1.1.2!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Steam Workshop Class Tree Modding'</strong> that gives players the power to create &amp; customize classes (live as of v1.1.0!)<br></li><li> <strong>'AI Challenges'</strong> with leaderboard support to bring fame to your hard-fought victories (live as of v1.0.16 &amp; v1.0.14!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Achievements &amp; Trading Cards'</strong> to round out the Steam game experience (live as of v1.0.16 &amp; v1.0.13!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Spectator Mode'</strong> to set the AI on autopilot and relax as the melee unfolds (live as of v1.0.12!)</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_updated_store_banner.png?t=1653929076\" /><br><br>In the tradition of Street Fighter II, Warcraft II, Bomberman 2, Seiken Densetsu 2 and other greats you may not have played until they hit with part two, we present <strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> - a game for those who like a little variety in their job system arena combat.<br><br>Check out the Demo if you want to try it first!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Maiden No Longer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/c780ce5c54badb2cc526d77b82168a6eb0149cae.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Rush!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/fa016e4ce8abd3be3723ae375b47706a50ffa1dc.jpg"},{"name":"You Keep Playing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/424ca435c096f56f585d953d03fd2859c9b1ac37.jpg"},{"name":"LAN Party","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/8eb56f89b5e701d63fdcdbe327f2b26fdf220cc1.jpg"},{"name":"Spectator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/e4c187f1dba6b9e3f739d70a3c4233a31125c7ed.jpg"},{"name":"You Must Like This Game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/842d6b0a055690057208877c55bd3cb31200f8f2.jpg"},{"name":"One Man Army","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/340440/8cbb6672c371d79f71220349ac7a3b982a3aae10.jpg"},{"name":"Close Shave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steams